Cloakfox: register CloakfoxMath JSWindowActor.

Adds the CloakfoxMath actor to the declarative JSWINDOWACTORS table in
ActorManagerParent. Fires on DOMWindowCreated for every http/https/file
document, runs with chrome principal in the content process, spoofs
Math.PI / Math.E / trig family per userContextId. No extension involved.

Actor body ships at additions/browser/components/cloakfox/actors/
CloakfoxMath{Child,Parent}.sys.mjs → lands at resource:///actors/ via
FINAL_TARGET_FILES.actors in that dir's moz.build.

Gated on cloakfox.enabled pref — the child actor checks this at entry
and bails if unset, so the actor stays resident but has zero impact
when Cloakfox is disabled.

